mLMegE (Pacman (PacState(i,(x,y),ve,L,p,l) c b Mega)) m | ((y == 0) && (x == (div (length m) 2))) = Pacman (PacState (i,(x,(lengthCorridor m) - 1),ve,L,p,l) (c-1) Closed Mega)
