mUMeg (Pacman (PacState (i,(x,y),ve,U,p,l) c b Mega)) m | (pieceInFrontP (x,y) U m) == Empty = Pacman (PacState (i,(x-1,y),ve,U,p,l) (c-1) Closed Mega)
